{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0Mzc4NDkyMDIw", "number": 6286, "title": "ace patch fixing issue when scrolling to end", "bodyText": "When we last updated Ace, we discovered that, when attempting to click in a document to place the caret at a particular position, the caret would often be placed above the clicked line. We fixed this initially by rounding the row height computed for a line widget:\nrstudio/rstudio-ace@7d1d7da\nHowever, this caused a separate regression where users could no longer scroll to the bottom of a document containing line widgets, as we had now computed a row height that was incongruent with the actual height of the widget.\nThe fix here is to instead avoid rounding in these computations altogether.\nSee also: rstudio/rstudio-ace@f2fe731\nCloses #6261.", "createdAt": "2020-02-21T22:03:33Z", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/6286", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "0f9fa2b1f2206e0c811051846ff1175c3024fd02"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-02-22T01:06:26Z", "author": {"login": "kevinushey"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 5, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcGnB_bAH2gAyMzc4NDkyMDIwOjAzY2U4YjFkZDlhMzMyZjdhNTllNWRlZmIzZDI3MTUyMWE5MGZhMzg=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcGpt2cgH2gAyMzc4NDkyMDIwOmQxNDI2MjI1YWM5MGQwMDYzODVlOWQ0ZjkzYzQyNWIwZWRhODg5NTY=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "03ce8b1dd9a332f7a59e5defb3d271521a90fa38", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/03ce8b1dd9a332f7a59e5defb3d271521a90fa38", "committedDate": "2020-02-21T21:58:06Z", "message": "ace patch fixing issue when scrolling to end"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "a21c78428efc6bab46247dc34c6be2f75d10b2bd", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/c